### Obtener todos los logins
GET {{baseUrl}}/Login
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener login por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/Login/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener login por usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/Login/usuario/admin
Content-Type: application/json

### Validar login (autenticaci√≥n)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Login/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuario": "admin",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Crear nuevo login
POST {{baseUrl}}/Login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuario": "nuevo_usuario",
    "pass": "nueva_password",
    "estado": true
}

### Actualizar login
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Login/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "idLogin": 1,
    "usuario": "usuario_actualizado",
    "pass": "password_actualizada",
    "estado": true
}

### Eliminar login (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Login/1
Content-Type: application/json 